  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Broken Wings: Hornet Down</strong> is a first person horror-adventure game set in a desert environment in the war-torn Afghanistan.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore your surroundings, interact with objects, unlock every part of the abandoned military complex. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But most importantly, find a way to call for help or you might stay here forever.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3395250/extras/70ba7ac3ce05468b309b2bcdf7942802.poster.avif?t=1738598850\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3395250/extras/70ba7ac3ce05468b309b2bcdf7942802.webm?t=1738598850\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3395250/extras/70ba7ac3ce05468b309b2bcdf7942802.mp4?t=1738598850\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The notes of the former inhabitants of the place will guide you through the unknown and will reveal the secrets of the previous war.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3395250/extras/ba3337fcd65e2debc84a8644ec729a49.poster.avif?t=1738598850\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3395250/extras/ba3337fcd65e2debc84a8644ec729a49.webm?t=1738598850\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3395250/extras/ba3337fcd65e2debc84a8644ec729a49.mp4?t=1738598850\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When the darkness falls, our hero is forced to seek shelter, however, his already desperate situation rapidly becomes much more sinister, as the history of the place comes alive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >During his struggle to explore the abandoned military complex, the story of another era unfolds. He quickly realizes he is not alone even though the outpost is empty for decades.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Who is this unknown creature?</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Broken Wings: Hornet Down</strong> is a first person horror-adventure game set in a desert environment in the war-torn Afghanistan.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore your surroundings, interact with objects, unlock every part of the abandoned military complex. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But most importantly, find a way to call for help or you might stay here forever.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3395250/extras/70ba7ac3ce05468b309b2bcdf7942802.poster.avif?t=1738598850\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3395250/extras/70ba7ac3ce05468b309b2bcdf7942802.webm?t=1738598850\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3395250/extras/70ba7ac3ce05468b309b2bcdf7942802.mp4?t=1738598850\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The notes of the former inhabitants of the place will guide you through the unknown and will reveal the secrets of the previous war.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3395250/extras/ba3337fcd65e2debc84a8644ec729a49.poster.avif?t=1738598850\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3395250/extras/ba3337fcd65e2debc84a8644ec729a49.webm?t=1738598850\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3395250/extras/ba3337fcd65e2debc84a8644ec729a49.mp4?t=1738598850\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When the darkness falls, our hero is forced to seek shelter, however, his already desperate situation rapidly becomes much more sinister, as the history of the place comes alive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >During his struggle to explore the abandoned military complex, the story of another era unfolds. He quickly realizes he is not alone even though the outpost is empty for decades.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Who is this unknown creature?</p>",
